Package: PolyAseqTrap
Type: Package
Title: PolyAseqTrap: a universal tool for genome-wide identification and quantification of polyadenylation sites from different 3’ end sequencing data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Wenbin Ye, Xin Cheng and Xiaohui Wu
Maintainer: Wenbin Ye <nikou123456@outlook.com>
Description: This package provides functions for identifying and quantifying polyA sites from different 3’ seq data.
